==English==

===Etymology===
A [[Latinisation]] of [[Alice]], which is in turn from the {{Ger.}} ''[[Adalheidis]]'' (from the Germanic ''*adal'', meaning ''noble'', and ''*heid'', meaning ''type''), via the {{OF.}} ''[[Adelais]]''.

